  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Wait and See! is a platform game developed by Dragon Co.. The game has Nu, pogodi! (Ну, погоди!, a famous Russian series of theatrical shorts similar to American series, Tom and Jerry) as an alternate title; however, apart from this and one of the cartridge labels, it has nothing to do with the actual cartoon.\n\nThe phrase \"Nu, pogodi!\" is more closely translated as \"Well, Just you wait!\" instead of \"Wait and see!\".\n\nBugs Bunny is featured in the title screen, despite that there's no references to Looney Tunes in the entire game.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    }
